high_descs: Turn left and walk around to face the foot of the bed.
Pick up the media player on the left side of the bed.
Walk around the right side of the bed to face the night stand.
Place the media device on the night table.
Turn around and walk around to face the foot of the bed.
Pick up the remaining media device on the bed.
Walk around the right side of the bed to face the night stand.
Place the media device on the night table next to the first media device.
anns.task_desc: To move two media devices to the night stand on the right side of the bed.

high_descs: Go around the bed to the foot of the bed.
Pick up the phone behind the red magazine on the bed.
Turn right to go around the bed to the black end table.
Place the phone on the top of the pencil on the top of the end table.
Go back to the foot of the bed.
Pick up the phone on the middle of the bed.
Go around the bed too go back to the end table.
Place the phone on the top of the end table on the right of the previous phone.
anns.task_desc: Move the phones from the bed to the end table.

high_descs: Go forward toward the bed, then turn left and move forward, then turn right, then turn right to face the bed.
Pick up the cell phone on the bed, next to the book.
Turn right and move forward to the desk, then turn left and go to the nightstand ahead.
Put the cell phone on the nightstand, in front of the pencil.
Turn around, go straight, then turn right to go around the bed, then turn right to face the bed.
Pick up the cell phone on the bed.
Turn right and move forward to the desk, then turn left and go to the nightstand ahead.
Put the cell phone on the nightstand, in front of the CD.
anns.task_desc: Move two cell phones to the nightstand.
